body_html:
Tensorflow is not compatible with Python 3.7 for now because it depends on a version of protobuf which does not support Python 3.7.
protobuf does not have a stable release that supports Python 3.7.
There are already many duplicated issues about 3.7 support: e.g. #20444 (comment), #20950

body:
Tensorflow __is not__ compatible with Python 3.7 for now because it depends on a version of protobuf which does not support Python 3.7.
protobuf does not have a stable release that supports Python 3.7.
There are already many duplicated issues about 3.7 support: e.g. https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/20444#issuecomment-428332353, https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/20950
